- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language specifications and semantic parsing. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper involves the use of neural networks for program synthesis. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the training of a neural synthesizer. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper deals with program synthesis, which is a software engineering task. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses incorporating code idioms into the underlying language for neural synthesis.
